Package: mycat
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6, libxcb-cursor0, libgl1, libegl1, libglib2.0-0, libxkbcommon0, fontconfig
Maintainer: yumiaura <yumiaura@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/yumiaura/myCat
Description: tiny animated desktop pet cat
 A small cat that sits on your desktop, blinks, follows your cursor, and flies
 little reminder banners across the screen. This is a self-contained build that
 bundles its own Python runtime and Qt, so no extra Python packages are needed.
